Tseshe.

501
00:24:53,466 --> 00:24:55,538
un vos iz geven ir nomen?

502
00:24:55,538 --> 00:24:57,274
di farheyrate nomen?

503
00:24:57,280 --> 00:24:59,670
farheyratn, ⟨TUSZYNSKI⟩.

504
00:25:00,402 --> 00:25:01,999
un ir man's nomen?

505
00:25:02,663 --> 00:25:06,116
⟨dem⟩ man's nomen iz gevezn

506
00:25:06,696 --> 00:25:08,074
gedenk shoyn nisht.

507
00:25:15,741 --> 00:25:17,169
ikh gedenk nisht.

508
00:25:18,627 --> 00:25:20,916
ven hostu getrofn dayn man?

509
00:25:21,462 --> 00:25:23,498
ven ikh hob getrofn mayn man?

510
00:25:24,718 --> 00:25:26,568
in TOMASZOW

511
00:25:27,520 --> 00:25:29,826
ven ikh bin geven a yung meydl

512
00:25:31,401 --> 00:25:33,724
hob ikh gehat a sakh ⟨POWODZENIA⟩

513
00:25:34,877 --> 00:25:40,237
der BOY hot mikh gevolt, der BOY, shkheynim vos hobn oykh gevoynt in di STREET

514
00:25:42,066 --> 00:25:44,459
un eyn mol hob ikh

515
00:25:44,459 --> 00:25:47,307
bin ikh gevezn epes in a park

516
00:25:48,597 --> 00:25:50,869
hob ikh bakent mayn man.

517
00:25:52,123 --> 00:25:55,829
hot er mikh nokhn, nokh di PARTY

518
00:25:56,106 --> 00:26:00,808
hot er mikh ongenumen bay di hant, un er iz aroysgeganen mit mir

519
00:26:01,995 --> 00:26:05,938
zogt er "ikh volt dikh gevolt hobn bite far a kale."

520
00:26:09,403 --> 00:26:11,979
hob ikh nisht gevust vos UNK tsu entfern.

521
00:26:15,090 --> 00:26:19,809
un azoy hot er ongehoybn arayntsukumen tsu undz in di shtub arayn.

522
00:26:20,389 --> 00:26:23,015
ikh hob gevoynt bay mayne eltern

523
00:26:24,203 --> 00:26:26,306
un azoy tsebislekh

524
00:26:27,983 --> 00:26:29,833
hot men khasene gehat.

525
00:26:29,788 --> 00:26:31,182
in velkhn yor?

526
00:26:31,375 --> 00:26:32,381
he?

527
00:26:32,033 --> 00:26:33,748
in velekhe yor?

528
00:26:34,075 --> 00:26:37,123
in velekhn yor? UNK ikh gedenk

529
00:26:38,378 --> 00:26:40,009
vi alt bistu geven?

530
00:26:40,285 --> 00:26:43,167
vi alt ikh bin gevezn denstmol?

531
00:26:43,167 --> 00:26:45,443
hob ikh gekent zayn efsher

532
00:26:47,895 --> 00:26:51,669
efsh- efsher fuftsn yor, efsher

533
00:26:52,772 --> 00:26:54,825
efsher fuftsn yor.

534
00:26:56,046 --> 00:27:01,608
nor, nu, er iz arayngekumen tsu undz in di shtub arayn

535
00:27:02,847 --> 00:27:06,114
un er hot arayngebrengt mayn sveter

536
00:27:06,610 --> 00:27:07,954
a sveter

537
00:27:08,989 --> 00:27:11,733
hot er mir arayngebrengt far mir

538
00:27:11,892 --> 00:27:13,303
ontsutun.

539
00:27:13,950 --> 00:27:16,644
kh'hob epes nisht gevolt nemen

540
00:27:17,258 --> 00:27:19,310
nor dokh zogt er "nem es."

541
00:27:20,481 --> 00:27:21,842
azoy hob ikh

542
00:27:22,067 --> 00:27:26,820
⟨bin ikh⟩ shoyn geganen. er iz arayngekumen tsu undz in shtub arayn

543
00:27:27,754 --> 00:27:30,431
un biz mayn tate

544
00:27:31,247 --> 00:27:35,699
hot gehaltn bay opshtarbn. er hot gehat a CANCER

545
00:27:35,699 --> 00:27:37,349
der tate mayner.

546
00:27:40,731 --> 00:27:43,745
hobn, hot gevoynt a shokhn

547
00:27:44,022 --> 00:27:45,366
a RABBI

548
00:27:46,468 --> 00:27:50,579
iz er flegt araynkumen zikh fregn vos der tate makht

549
00:27:52,257 --> 00:27:55,980
ts- ruft er mikh avek un zogt tsu mir azoy.

550
00:27:56,239 --> 00:27:57,667
"Leyele

551
00:27:58,163 --> 00:28:01,076
der tate halt bay opshtarbn.

552
00:28:01,504 --> 00:28:04,822
ikh vil az du zolst nemen khupe kidushn

553
00:28:05,284 --> 00:28:07,190
far der tate shtarbt."

554
00:28:07,190 --> 00:28:08,510
un azoy iz geven.

555
00:28:08,510 --> 00:28:10,813
un dos iz geven mayn khasene.

556
00:28:11,427 --> 00:28:13,615
kh'hob nisht gehat keyn khasene.

557
00:28:14,818 --> 00:28:18,474
kh'hob genumen khupe kidushn barn tatn's bet.

558
00:28:19,392 --> 00:28:21,242
dos iz geven mayn lebn.

559
00:28:25,264 --> 00:28:27,772
kh'hob a sakh mitgemakht in lebn.

560
00:28:28,318 --> 00:28:29,864
zeyer a sakh.

561
00:28:32,807 --> 00:28:34,066
un ikh gedenk

562
00:28:34,123 --> 00:28:36,699
ven m'iz gegebn in Rusland

563
00:28:36,756 --> 00:28:39,517
vi s'hot gekontshet zikh di milkhome

564
00:28:40,283 --> 00:28:41,571
in Rusland

565
00:28:41,571 --> 00:28:44,108
velekhes yor iz dos gevezn?

566
00:28:44,822 --> 00:28:46,318
ikh gedenk shoyn nisht.

567
00:28:48,957 --> 00:28:52,379
hob ikh gezogt ikh vil forn aheym.

568
00:28:52,379 --> 00:28:54,671
ikh vil nisht zayn in Rusland.

569
00:28:56,753 --> 00:28:58,181
hot men mir

570
00:28:58,963 --> 00:29:00,825
aroyfgesh-

571
00:29:00,825 --> 00:29:03,530
-shtelt oyf, oyf di shif

572
00:29:04,515 --> 00:29:06,264
in Rusland

573
00:29:07,266 --> 00:29:10,601
hot men mikh aroyfgeshtelt oyf di shif

574
00:29:10,928 --> 00:29:13,200
un m'hot mir epes gegebn epes

575
00:29:13,273 --> 00:29:16,594
a por zl- a por zlotes tsi

576
00:29:16,594 --> 00:29:17,975
a por rubl

577
00:29:19,213 --> 00:29:21,536
un m'iz geforn keyn Poyln.

578
00:29:22,048 --> 00:29:28,302
kh'hob a sakh mitgemakht in lebn. dos, der kop ken nisht azoy fil far- gedenken ales.

579
00:29:28,596 --> 00:29:31,190
me kumt tsu di ende fun di ershte TAPE.

580
00:29:31,077 --> 00:29:31,833
he?

581
00:29:31,896 --> 00:29:34,956
me kumt tsu di ende fun di ershte TAPE.

